      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "advantage, how do I rethink my existing sources of competitive advantage?",
      "x": 384.8,
      "y": 153.7,
      "w": 509.9,
      "h": 17.9,
      "font": "HendersonBCGSans-Light",
      "size": 16.0,
      "color": "#000000",
      "flags": 0
    },
    {
      "text": "How do I upskill people to drive adoption while also retaining critical ",
